abstract: After a strike by workers and other production setbacks, Boeing confirmed it would push back deliveries of its new jet, the 787 Dreamliner, until the first quarter of 2010.
snippet: After a strike by workers and other production setbacks, Boeing confirmed it would push back deliveries of its new jet, the 787 Dreamliner, until the first quarter of 2010.
lead_paragraph: The Boeing Company confirmed on Thursday that it would delay deliveries of its new jet, the 787, until the first quarter of 2010.

headline.main: Boeing Delays Delivery of the 787 to 2010
